OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAsk patients about         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fgambling, health guidance  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fsays                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Doctors should ask people with a       
OL,6, mental-health problem about their      
OL,7, gambling habits to identify those who  
OL,8, need help, draft health guidance says. 
OL,10,FIt adds that with problem gamblers, GPs
OL,11,Fshould discuss software to limit online
OL,12,Fgambling and talking therapy treatment 
OL,13,Fat an early stage.                     
OL,15,FPatients can be referred to one of 12  
OL,16,FNHS gambling-treatment clinics in      
OL,17,FEngland, with three more planned.      
OL,19,FSome 300,000 UK adults are problem     
OL,20,Fgamblers, a recent review found.       
